{"tid":1684519,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名宿：美斯若想證明比C.朗強 轉會去皇馬","createTime":"2019-10-31T06:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T15:51:58.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"190dd85154ef13462df583b39ae78e6399f2e53e","tid":1684519,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"「美C」到底誰更出色？近10年來，足球界都在為了這個問題而爭論不休。近日阿根廷傳奇門將烏戈-加蒂（Hugo Gatti）在接受採訪時表示，美斯（Lionel Messi）要想證明自己比C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）出色，唯一的途徑就是轉會去皇馬，證明C.朗拿度的那些成就他也能做到。<br />\n<br />\n  加蒂在參加一檔名為El Chiringuito de Jugones的電視節目時表示：「似乎我是一個反阿根廷主義者，但在美斯沒有在一些重要比賽中表現出色之前，我依然認為他是一名主場型球員。他需要轉會去皇馬，然後在那裡證明C.朗拿度做到的那些事情他也能做到。否則的話，他只是一名比較出色的球員罷了。」<br />\n<br />\n報導截圖<br />\n<br />\n  加蒂繼續說道：「C.朗拿度去了世界上最好的球隊，但美斯一直在主場踢球，在他的舒適圈中踢球。讓他去歐冠盃和世界盃等重要比賽中踢球吧，否則他只是芸芸眾生中的一個。當他在那裡拿出好的表現時，他才有資格和告魯夫（Johan Cruijff）、馬勒當拿（Maradona）和比利（Pele）等傳奇一較高下。」<br />\n<br />\n加蒂在節目中談論美斯C.朗拿度<br />\n<br />\n  對於今年的金球獎應該歸誰這個問題，加蒂表示：「在自己的家中踢球，一切條件都舒舒服服的，那根本不是什麼難事。讓我們看看美斯在歐聯關鍵戰中的表現吧，這樣才能看出他是否值得我們為他投票。」<br />\n<br />\n  加蒂是阿根廷的傳奇門將，是上世紀70年代末80年代初小保加的主力門將，為球隊出場超過300次，也為阿根廷國家隊出場過18次。"},{"pid":"1d51cd6b5b6ac26fca362e7364fecbb35ab6e8ca","tid":1684519,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美斯: 明明大家西甲10年，我贏佢7次喎"},{"pid":"43aee189605614278f85e82e3cedef6117caa25c","tid":1684519,"uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1d51cd6b5b6ac26fca362e7364fecbb35ab6e8ca","tid":1684519,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美斯: 明明大家西甲10年，我贏佢7次喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"證明巴塞隊友勁姐"},{"pid":"669711d1795dc22c831de02118c428fc245bf201","tid":1684519,"uid":247666,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"C朗若想證明比美斯強 轉會去巴塞"},{"pid":"a5ff272c56db045f4a53f23e88dab73b179d2258","tid":1684519,"uid":89923,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"美斯若想證明比我強, 黎香港跟隊, 否則只能算是好球員"},{"pid":"73b93d1a3c02d27b8afd616c8be709f6fa9ac106","tid":1684519,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d51cd6b5b6ac26fca362e7364fecbb35ab6e8ca","tid":1684519,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美斯: 明明大家西甲10年，我贏佢7次喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"C朗若想證明比美斯強 踢贏C朗7季"},{"pid":"3ac976d1cab5d4854d0b00d8d67927fb6c84c77a","tid":1684519,"uid":34419,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"美斯若想證明比陳7強 轉會去南華"},{"pid":"578d852e3ed3552f4c95a4b110ce0bba43fb8962","tid":1684519,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"4個字,溫室小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cff0bd4b43239528b55327adc3e44c0a81e300c","tid":1684519,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e595300b7ff6a98a32db86f9b74ee6f22dedb7","tid":1684519,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ac976d1cab5d4854d0b00d8d6792